Step 4- Add User & Give Access

Add Users and give access

Note: Sample was done with the name Alumni workspace

At this stage the report is ready to be shared and make sure with whom the report could be shared

If the report is ready to be shared manage permissions could be given to do this:

- the user need to have an e-mail Id to grant access

- roles should be defined , to share, read or build

- Add or remove access can be done
